</taxonomicName>
sp.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,925,1466]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
Record based on a photo taken by P. Wirtz at Caniço de Baixo in 
<quantity box="[968,1028,1160,1186]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" unit="m" value="20.0">20 m</quantity>
depth, at night (figure 
<number box="[1300,1317,1160,1186]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="2.0">2</number>
). A. Brito (personal communication, 
<date box="[467,585,1200,1226]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="2005-10">
Oct. 
<number box="[525,585,1200,1226]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="2005.0">2005</number>
</date>
) tentatively identified this as 
<taxonomicName authority="Peters, 1877" authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1877" box="[939,1402,1200,1226]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Ophichthidae" genus="Apterichtus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Anguilliformes" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="anguiformis">
<emphasis box="[939,1225,1200,1225]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Apterichtus anguiformis</emphasis>
(Peters, 
<number box="[1330,1393,1200,1226]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1877.0">1877</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
. A specimen is needed to confirm the identification. New record for Madeira.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,925,1466]" box="[197,908,1280,1306]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis box="[197,435,1280,1305]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
* 
<taxonomicName authority="Linnaeus, 1758" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" box="[209,435,1280,1305]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Ophichthidae" genus="Apterichtus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Anguilliformes" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="caecus">Apterichtus caecus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(Linnaeus, 
<number box="[573,629,1280,1306]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1758.0">1758</number>
)—European finless eel
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,925,1466]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
Record based on 
<accessionNumber box="[400,549,1320,1346]" httpUri="http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/MMF25419" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<collectionCode box="[400,469,1320,1346]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/mme0-gx6r" name="Museu Municipal do Funchal" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">MMF</collectionCode>
<number box="[476,549,1320,1346]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="25419.0">25419</number>
</accessionNumber>
and 
<number box="[607,680,1320,1346]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="33856.0">33856</number>
